"\"<p data-start=\\\"225\\\" data-end=\\\"440\\\">In today\u2019s high-pressure workplace, burnout is expensive\u2014and disengagement costs more than we think. This webinar explores why employee well-being is no longer a \u201cnice-to-have,\u201d but a strategic business advantage.<\/p><p data-start=\\\"225\\\" data-end=\\\"440\\\"><br><\/p>\\n<p data-start=\\\"442\\\" data-end=\\\"715\\\">Join us as we unpack how a healthy workplace culture directly impacts <b>performance<\/b>, <b>productivity<\/b>, <b>retention<\/b>, and <b>long-term profitability<\/b>. Learn how organizations that prioritize well-being don\u2019t just create happier employees\u2014they build stronger, more resilient businesses.<\/p><p data-start=\\\"442\\\" data-end=\\\"715\\\"><br><\/p>\\n<p data-start=\\\"717\\\" data-end=\\\"942\\\"><b><i>Whether you\u2019re a leader, HR professional, or people manager<\/i><\/b>, this session will challenge traditional mindsets and show why investing in people delivers real, measurable returns. Because when people thrive, business follows.<\/p>\""